<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.9">
<l>mēkalaiyāṟ kuṟaivillā melivuṟṟa vakalalkul</l>
<l>pōkamakaḷ pukaḻttantai viṟalvāṇaṉ puyantuṇittu</l>
<l>nākamicait tuyilvāṉpō lulakellā naṉkoṭuṅka</l>
<l>yōkaṇaivāṉ kavarāta vuṭampiṉāṟ kuṟaivilamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except the want for [our] girdle</l>
<l>we have no want for [our] body that is not seized by the one who has a support in Yoga,</l>
<l>in order to keep all the worlds well restrained, like one who sleeps on the serpent,</l>
<l>cutting off the arm of victorious Bhāṇa, famous father of the daughter of enjoyment,</l>
	<l>with slender broad hips.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
